msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&वाम;</shortcut> <guimenu>नेविगेशन</guimenu> <guimenuitem>वामगन्तु</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "This action will move the selection cursor to the left."
msgstr "एषा क्रिया चयनकर्सरं वामभागे गमिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Right;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigation</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Right</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Right;</shortcut> <guimenu>नेविगेशन</guimenu> <guimenuitem>दक्षिणं "
"गच्छतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "This action will move the selection cursor to the right."
msgstr "एषा क्रिया चयनकर्सरं दक्षिणतः गमिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Up;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigation</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Up</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Up;</shortcut> <guimenu>नेविगेशन</guimenu> <guimenuitem>ऊर्ध्वं गच्छतु</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "This action will move the selection cursor up."
msgstr "एषा क्रिया चयनकर्सरं उपरि गमिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Down;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigation</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Down</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Down;</shortcut> <guimenu>नेविगेशन</guimenu> <guimenuitem>अधः गच्छतु</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "This action will move the selection cursor down."
msgstr "एषा क्रिया चयनकर्सरं अधः गमिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Space;</shortcut> <guimenu>Navigation</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Select</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Space;</shortcut> <guimenu>नेविगेशन</guimenu> <guimenuitem>चयनं</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "This action will select the item currently under the cursor."
msgstr "एषा क्रिया कर्सरस्य अधः वर्तमानं द्रव्यं चिनोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>अग्रे दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggles the information on next marbles."
msgstr "अग्रिम-संगमरवरेषु सूचनां टॉग्ल् करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kolorlines; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"अतिरिक्तरूपेण &kolorlines; सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> तथा "
"<guimenu>सहायता</guimenu> मेनू-वस्तूनाम्, अधिकसूचनार्थं <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">सेटिंग्स् मेन्यू< इत्यस्य विषये विभागान् पठन्तु /"
"ulink> तथा च &kde; मौलिकता।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "बहुधा पृष्टाः प्रश्नाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "अहम् अस्य क्रीडायाः स्वरूपं परिवर्तयितुम् इच्छामि। अहं शक्नोमि ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change &kolorlines; visual theme you can use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kolorlines;…"
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"आम्‌। परिवर्तनार्थं &kolorlines; दृश्यविषयं भवान् <menuchoice><guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>&kolorlines;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> मेनू-वस्तु विन्यस्तुं "
"उपयोक्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "I don't want to make any moves right now. Can I skip a turn?"
msgstr "अहम् अधुना किमपि चालनं कर्तुम् न इच्छामि। किं अहं एकं वारं लङ्घयितुं शक्नोमि ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To skip a turn you can use a <link linkend=\"menu-move-endturn"
"\">keyboard shortcut</link>, or a <link linkend=\"menu-move-endturn"
"\">menubar</link> option."
msgstr ""
"आम्‌। एकं वारं त्यक्तुं भवन्तः a<link linkend=\"menu-move-endturn\"> कीबोर्ड शॉर्टकट</"
"link> , अथवा क<link linkend=\"menu-move-endturn\"> menubar</link> विकल्प।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "क्रीडां कर्तुं कीबोर्डस्य उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नोमि वा?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. You can use the cursor keys and the &Space; key to select and set the "
"marbles."
msgstr "आम्‌। भवान् कर्सर-कील्स् तथा &Space; मार्बल्स् चयनं सेट् च कर्तुं कीलम्।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "अत्र किं कर्तव्यमिति चिन्तयितुं न शक्नोमि! किं संकेताः सन्ति ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kolorlines; does not have a <quote>Hint</quote> feature."
msgstr "सं.&kolorlines; <quote>Hint</quote> इति विशेषता नास्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"इदानीं मया क्रीडां त्यक्तव्या, परन्तु अहम् अद्यापि न समाप्तः। अहं मम प्रगतिम् रक्षितुं शक्नोमि "
"वा ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kolorlines; does not have a <quote>Save</quote> feature at the moment."
msgstr "&kolorlines; अस्मिन् क्षणे <quote>रक्षतु</quote> इति विशेषता नास्ति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "गेम विन्यास"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kolorlines; configuration dialog allows you to select &kolorlines; visual "
"themes."
msgstr "&kolorlines; विन्याससंवादः भवन्तं &kolorlines; दृश्यविषयाः।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select a new theme simply choose the theme from the selection list. Each "
"item in the list shows a small preview left to the theme name. A selection "
"is immediately applied."
msgstr ""
"नूतनं विषयं चयनं कर्तुं केवलं चयनसूचिकातः विषयं चिनोतु । सूचीस्थं प्रत्येकं द्रव्यं विषयनामस्य "
"अवशिष्टं लघु पूर्वावलोकनं दर्शयति । तत्क्षणमेव चयनं प्रयुक्तं भवति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you are satisfied with the theme you have selected you can click the "
"<guibutton>Close</guibutton>, located at the bottom part of this dialog."
msgstr ""
"एकवारं भवता चयनितविषयेण सन्तुष्टः जातः चेत् भवान् अस्य संवादस्य अधः भागे स्थितं "
"<guibutton>Close</guibutton> नुदतु ।"

